ws = op.Workspace()
ws.clear()
pn = op.network.Cubic(shape=[3, 3, 3])
op.io.OpenpnmIO.save_workspace(filename='test.pnm')
ws = op.io.OpenpnmIO.load_workspace(filename='test.pnm', overwrite=True)
assert len(ws.keys()) == 1
ws = op.io.OpenpnmIO.load_workspace(filename='test.pnm', overwrite=False)
assert len(ws.keys()) == 2
assert isinstance(ws, op.Workspace)
